# id: Validator -> void validate(Object target, Errors errors)_
commentText:
Validate the supplied target object, which must be_of a {@link Class} for which the {@link #supports(Class)} method_typically has (or would) return true._

The supplied {@link Errors errors} instance can be used to report_any resulting validation errors._@param target the object that is to be validated (can be null)_@param errors contextual state about the validation process (never null)_@see ValidationUtils
